 magaabowta Sinam Yallih Buxaaxik Buxak teynal Yallih yab kawisak sittin fanal 
gacisak Sakiina keenil obteh akke waytek, Racmat ken buuleh akke waytek
 Malaaika ken marisseh akke waytek, Ylli isi garih marah ken gabbaaqeh 
akke waytek, Taama teydeere Num tokkek oslè maqaane kaa maxayyossa)) 
tamannal xaagossem Muslim kinni.
Tama Cadiisik kaxxa Muxxo kinni geynu dudnam, Muslimtuh adda yableenim
