kah teellek. Nummasseh iyye.Cakkumu inne isih isserah isih nummaysa.
iyyeh : yoh warisey imaaninna ? iyyeh : Taamineemi Yallal kay Malaa-ikal
 kay kitoobal, kay Farmoytittel, illacaboh ayrol, taamineemi kay Cukmil
