saytunnoysan innah dambittek
addunya buxak tayse buxa kaah abaay , akeerah ahali addunyah ahlik
yayse ahli kaah ab. Kaadu jannat kaa culusaay qhabri digaalaa kee gira
digaalak kaa cat, kaadu qhabri adda kaah fakaay kay adda kaah nooris
iyya; Yi Rabbow kay galto caraamu nel 
maabinaay , kay lakal nee mamakkoysin
tohuk lakal ferey haytoh adda takbiirat aba, tama takbiiratih lakal
inki adda migdal salaamat gacsa.
